Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, binutils, gcc, libc6, libgcc-s1
Provides: rustc (= ${binary:Version})
Replaces: rustc
Description: Rust systems programming language @MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@
 Rust is a curly-brace, block-structured expression language. It visually
 resembles the C language family, but differs significantly in syntactic and
 semantic details. This package provides the Rust @MAJOR_MINOR_VERSION@.x
 compiler, rustdoc, and standard library.
